\sigma\left(n\right)=\prod_{j=1}^{m}\left(1+p_{j}+\dots+p_{j}^{k_{j}}\right)=\prod_{j=1}^{m}\frac{p_{j}^{k_{j}+1}-1}{p_{j}-1}.\label{eq:sum-of-divisors}
