\end_layout

\end_inset

Заменим конечную сумму 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{d=1}^{N}\frac{\mu\left(d\right)}{d^{2}}$
\end_inset

 рядом 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{d=1}^{\infty}\frac{\mu\left(d\right)}{d^{2}}$
\end_inset

.
 При этом будет совершена ошибка не более 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{k>N}\frac{1}{k^{2}}\le\frac{1}{N}$
\end_inset

 (по формуле 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:rest-of-sum-of-inverse-squares"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
По 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:sum-of-moebius-and-inverser-of-zeta"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 и 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:zeta-of-2n-no-proof"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
